If you don't like action and want good story line, great dialogues etc etc then you'll not like it. Myself i enjoy a lot of different kind of films but this time i felt like seeing action and as such it's a good film.

When judging a film i think you have to consider the purpose of said film and the audience it's aimed at. If you can't look past your own taste then you shouldn't judge anything beyond the genres you like(as you're opinion will likely be useless to the people who enjoys said genre)
